videos.description: Kansas Forward Josh Jackson exits game and heads to locker room after landing awkwardly on his ankle. He would later return to the game.
videos.headline: Josh Jackson exits game after injuring his ankle

videos.description: Carlton Bragg Jr. grabs the offensive board and throws it down.
videos.headline: Bragg Jr. throws down the putback

videos.description: Carlton Bragg Jr. elevates for the putback dunk after TCU fails to box him out.
videos.headline: Bragg Jr. rattles the rim with a ferocious dunk

videos.description: Frank Mason III draws his defender in before drawing the foul and burying a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Mason III drains and-1 3-pointer from the wing

videos.description: Frank Mason III gets a standing ovation from Kansas faithful after burying a 3-pointer and staring down TCU.
videos.headline: Mason III buries a 3-pointer, stares down TCU

videos.description: Vladimir Brodziansky attempts the layup, but Carlton Bragg Jr. is having none of it.
videos.headline: Bragg Jr. destroys Brodziansky with a monster block

videos.description: Former Kansas and current Timberwolves guard Brandon Rush has his No. 25 jersey retired.
videos.headline: Brandon Rush gets his jersey retired during halftime.

videos.description: Frank Mason III throws up the lob, Josh Jackson does the rest.
videos.headline: Jackson obliterates the rim with a ferocious slam

videos.description: Lagerald Vick finds Landen Lucas with a sweet dime for the dunk as Kansas tries to pull away.
videos.headline: Lucas throws down the dunk

videos.description: Carlton Bragg Jr. dunks it down after the perfect feed from Josh Jackson.
videos.headline: Jackson finds Bragg Jr. inside with a pretty pass

videos.description: Lagerald Vick throws down the alley-oop and gets and-1 off a dime from Josh Jackson.
videos.headline: Jackson is dropping dimes with huge alley-oop to Vick

videos.description: Kansas puts the dagger in TCU with an incredible alley-oop.
videos.headline: Graham finds Jackson for the alley-oop

videos.description: strong performances from Josh Jackson and Frank Mason III lead Kansas to Big 12 championship.
videos.headline: Kansas routs TCU 87-68 to win 13th straight Big 12 title
